         <scopecontent>
      <head>Scope and Contents</head>
                  <p>The administrative records primarily pertain to the bank's 75th and 85th anniversaries, which were celebrated in 1951 and 1961. These files include correspondence, promotional material, photographs, pamphlets, and newspaper clippings. The records also include publicity files, which contain three scrapbooks with newspaper clippings of advertising campaign materials, as well as a campaign book for the bank's "Landmarks That Live" campaign. The organizations and conventions materials consist of a large scrapbook containing materials pertaining to the 48th and 49th annual conventions for the Texas Bankers Association.</p>
